  "type": "feat",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have started to develop Nature beyond other skills, delving deeper into its possibilities.</p><p><strong>Core Feats</strong></p><ul><li>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.TZDQM59QbGDLheEM]{Stifle Flames}</li></ul><p>Choose one Skill Path and gain that path's Trained feat.</p><p><strong>Available Skill Paths</strong></p><ul><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.Dh10O2syMwv1jsoD]{Spellcraft (Nature) Path - Trained}</strong>: Your excellent knowledge of spells helps you identifying spells with great success.</li><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.GQ1mBR00XTHPibAH]{Itemcraft (Nature) Path - Trained}</strong>: Your knowledge of magical items empowers you use them to beyond their limits.</li><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.jWczwUsZJhvv4y7D]{Wild Communion Path - Trained}</strong>: You have the unmatched ability to commune with animals and spirits.</li><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.UVI0W5YiTFi2j4LD]{Beast Handling Path - Trained}</strong>: You are a master in handling tamed beasts.</li><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.f16NuLoCBkFgm2lE]{Naturalist Path - Trained}</strong>: You know most of natures' opportunities to heal.</li></ul>",
